{{Quote|Far as I can see this job's not going to pay us anything more than all the cactus we can eat...and we had to go thru a barroom brawl to get the job, at that!|Han Solo|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 9">[[Star Wars (1977) 9|''Star Wars'' (1977) 9]]</ref>}}
'''Dune-cactus''', sometimes referred to simply as "'''cactus'''" was a species of [[Plant/Legends|plant]] found in the [[Desert/Legends|deserts]] of [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]]. It was the largest living thing [[Jimm Doshun]] had shot at with his [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] prior to joining the [[Star-Hoppers of Aduba-3|Sprites]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] did not consider the dune-cactus to be fit for eating.

